<plot>"Wang Zi Cheng Long", the old Chinese adage of transforming one's child into a dragon, is even more prevalent in modern-day China than ever before. In this revealing look into the extreme pressures placed on China's children today, we follow three children from vastly different backgrounds in their quest to fulfill their parents' increasingly high expectations.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?158950</url></doc>
